race.comment: MAGNA MAK (3) resumes with a good fresh record and will relish the claim. Back without a trial and gets map favours. Each-way. TIME ANGEL (10) went out fast and failed to grip on when fifth over 1000m at Gundagai. Fitter now in this easier contest. BARGINO (14) chipped away late when up in class for a close-up ninth over 1000m contest at this track. No shock to see him return to form. MER CHAR (6) strips fitter third-up and stays in the calculations after finishing fifth over 1175m at this track. Drawn out but has each way prospects. NOCI DI COCCO (16) much better effort at this course and distance when second at latest. Worth thought if he gains a start.
